NAME

DateTime::Locale::twq_NE - Locale data examples for the Tasawaq Niger (twq-NE) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Tasawaq Niger locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Atalaata 5 Feewiriye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Alzuma 22 Deesanbur 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Asibti 15 Sektanbur -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feewiriye 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Deesanbur 1995
